            {
              "id": "IC_kwDOFcwZ1c6Hd2Cr",
              "body": "### PR summary [ba32c4d3e0](https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/15582/commits/ba32c4d3e0f19b95cf644445db98ec8cfb1a323c)\n\n#### Import changes for modified files\n\nNo significant changes to the import graph\n\n\n<details><summary>Import changes for all files</summary>\n\n|Files|Import difference|\n|-|-|\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n<details><summary>\n\n#### Declarations diff\n\n</summary>\n\n`+ infinite_of_linearly_independent_coxeterWeight_four`\n`+ infinite_range_add_nsmul_iff`\n`+ infinite_range_add_smul_iff`\n`+ infinite_range_reflection_reflection_iterate_iff`\n`+ reflection_reflection_iterate`\n<details>\n  <summary>You can run this locally as follows</summary>\n\n\n```bash\n## summary with just the declaration names:\n./scripts/declarations_diff.sh <optional_commit>\n\n## more verbose report:\n./scripts/declarations_diff.sh long <optional_commit>\n```\n</details>\n\nThe doc-module for `script/declarations_diff.sh` contains some details about this script.\n\n</details>",
